---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="About EigenSelf"
	pubDate={new Date('June 02 2026')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		EigenSelf is a generative framework for self-understanding — sibling to systems like
		MBTI, IFS, or the Enneagram, but built from a values-network model rather than a fixed
		typology. The pipeline is short: a survey of the values that matter to you and how they
		connect, a set of graph analyses over that network, and a personal report that reflects
		the structure back to you.
	</p>
	<p>
		The framework is judged by resonance, generativity, and traceability back to what you
		actually said in the survey — not by test–retest scores. The reader is the validator.
	</p>
	<p>
		This site collects writing about the framework. The reports themselves are delivered
		privately to each reader.
	</p>
</Layout>
